title.en-US: Gray Baby Bib with Black Logo

description.en-US: Avoid getting food stains on child’s clothes with this baby bib. The reinforced hook & loop closure makes it easy to put on, but hard for baby to take off. 4x4" embroidered logo.

description.en-US: Lightweight and durable, this mug is a must-have for every devoted camper. Use it for your favorite beverage or a hot meal, and attach it to your bag for easy access on a hike. Ready for your next camping trip?
